:

*Piće* se sprema u kuhinji. (It is being prepared in the kitchen.)
Deca piju *piće*. (The children are drinking.)
On je prešao u drugu sobu da uzme *piće*. (He went to another room to get a drink.)
Ona je popila *piće*. (She drank the drink.)
Čuvaj *piće* u frižideru. (Keep the drink in the refrigerator.)